                            <comment id="15658027" author="aozeritsky" created="Fri, 11 Nov 2016 20:01:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The simplest way to fix it is to move complicated code (i.e. .appendMessagesToLeader) outside the lock. See PR&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15658044" author="aozeritsky" created="Fri, 11 Nov 2016 20:08:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As for now I think you can use the following config as a workaround&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;# 100 days
offsets.retention.minutes=144000
# 1 hour
offsets.retention.check.interval.ms=3600000
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
